50|$|From ITU, 1.145 <b>Spurious</b> emission: <b>Emission</b> on a {{frequency}} or frequencies which are outside thenecessary bandwidth {{and the level}} of which may be reduced without affecting the corresponding transmission of information. <b>Spurious</b> <b>emissions</b> include harmonic emissions, parasitic emissions, intermodulation products and frequency conversion products but exclude out-of-band emissions.|$|R
